ns><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[风邪]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[寒邪]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[暑邪]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[湿邪]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[燥邪]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[D]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：湿性重浊，浊多指分泌物、排泄物等秽浊不清。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>html</format><desc><![CDATA[5.<u><b>不属于</b></u>火邪的性质及致病特点是]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[凝滞主痛]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[其性炎上]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[易致肿疡]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[伤津耗气]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[生风动血]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[A]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：火邪的性质及致病特点是火为阳邪，其性炎上；火易伤津耗气；火易生风动血；火易致肿疡。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>html</format><desc><![CDATA[6.<u><b>不属于</b></u>疠气的致病特点是]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[传染性强]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[易于康复]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[一气一病]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[症状相似]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[发病急骤]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[B]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：疠气的致病特点是传染性强，易于流行；发病急骤，病情危重；一气一病，症状相似。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[7.大怒伤]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[心]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[肺]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[肝]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[脾]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[肾]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[C]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：大怒伤肝。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[8.七情内伤致病最易伤及的脏是]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[心肝脾]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[心肺脾]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[心肝肾]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[心肺肝]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[肺脾肾]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[A]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：七情的致病直接伤及内脏，在临床上最常见以影响心、肝、脾三脏为多见。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[9.与痰饮形成关系最密切的三脏是]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[心肺脾]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[肺脾肾]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[心肺肝]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[肺肝肾]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[肺脾肝]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[B]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：痰饮多由肺、脾、肾三脏功能失调，水液代谢障碍，以致水液停滞而成。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>html</format><desc><![CDATA[10.下列哪项<u><b>不是</b></u>瘀血的致病特点]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[固定不移的刺痛]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[疼痛昼轻夜重]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[局部青紫肿胀]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[疼痛部位喜温喜按]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[出血多紫黯或夹有血块]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[D]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：瘀血的致病特点为疼痛，多为刺痛，痛处固定不移，拒按，夜甚；肿块，肿块固定不移；出血，血色多紫黯，或夹有血块；发绀，面色黧黑或紫黯，肌肤甲错，口唇、爪甲青紫；舌紫黯，或有瘀点、瘀斑；脉涩或结代等。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[11.“实”的病机主要是指]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[正气不足]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[脏腑亏虚]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[功能旺盛]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[正气充实]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[邪气亢盛]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[E]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：实，主要指邪气亢盛，是以邪气盛为矛盾主要方面的一种病理反映。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[12.“虚”的病机主要是指]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[正气不足]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[脏腑亏虚]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[功能旺盛]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[正气充实]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[邪气亢盛]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[A]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：虚，主要指正气不足，是以正气虚为矛盾主要方面的一种病理反映。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[13.阴偏衰导致]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[虚寒证]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[实热证]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[虚热证]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[血虚证]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[阳虚证]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[C]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：阴偏衰，阴液不足，滋养、宁静和制约阳热的功能减退，可致阳气相对偏盛的虚热证。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[14.阳偏衰导致]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[虚寒证]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[实热证]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[虚热证]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[血虚证]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[阳虚证]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[A]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：阳偏衰，阳气不足，阳不制阴，阴相对亢盛的虚寒证。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>html</format><desc><![CDATA[15.<u><b>不属于</b></u>实证的临床表现是]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[二便不通]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[壮热狂躁]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[腹痛拒按]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[声高气粗]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[二便失禁]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[E]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：实证的临床表现是壮热狂躁、腹痛拒按、声高气粗、二便不通、脉实有力等。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[16.不属于虚证的临床表现是]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[神疲倦怠]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[心悸气短]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[二便不通]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[畏寒肢冷]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[脉虚无力]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[C]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：虚证的临床表现是神疲倦怠、面容憔悴、心悸气短、自汗盗汗、畏寒肢冷、脉虚无力。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[17.火热之邪致病可见]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[汗出恶风]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[高热、神昏谵语]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[头身困重、四肢倦怠]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[关节屈伸不利、拘挛疼痛]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[皮肤干涩]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[B]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：火易生风动血，火热之邪侵犯人体，灼伤津液，使筋脉失其濡养，而致肝风内动，表现为高热、神昏谵语、四肢抽搐、项背强直、角弓反张、目睛上视等症。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[18.湿邪致病可见]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[汗出恶风]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[高热、神昏谵语]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[头身困重、四肢倦怠]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[关节屈伸不利、拘挛疼痛]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[皮肤干涩]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[C]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：湿性重浊，重，体现在湿邪犯体，常使人感觉头身困重、四肢倦怠。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[19.风邪致病可见]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[汗出恶风]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[高热、神昏谵语]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[头身困重、四肢倦怠]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[关节屈伸不利、拘挛疼痛]]></desc></option><option><id>E</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[皮肤干涩]]></desc></option></options><answers><![CDATA[A]]></answers><keypoints><![CDATA[解析：风邪伤人易侵犯人体的头面、肌表等阳位，使腠理疏泄而开张，多见头痛、汗出、恶风等症。]]></keypoints></question><question><type>1</type><format>text</format><desc><![CDATA[20.有3名小学生先后出现发热、耳下腮部漫肿疼痛，经辨证分析，中医诊断为痄腮。导致痄腮发生的原因是]]></desc><options><option><id>A</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[六淫]]></desc></option><option><id>B</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[疠气]]></desc></option><option><id>C</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[七情]]></desc></option><option><id>D</id><type>text</type><desc><![CDATA[饮食]]></